  "detailed_description": "Frido is a simple 3D arcade game for kids and adults inspired by popular arcade games from the 2000s. The player will have to take control of a robot that has fallen into the past and do everything to help him return home. As the game progresses, you will need to collect parts and solve simple puzzles.<br>3D arcade game of moderate difficulty for the whole family.<br><br>• More than 10 exciting levels<br><br>• 3 biomes with unique traps and obstacles<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072910/extras/7d30d98e816f8c020dac48fa9ea237b3.poster.avif?t=1680275362\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072910/extras/7d30d98e816f8c020dac48fa9ea237b3.webm?t=1680275362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072910/extras/7d30d98e816f8c020dac48fa9ea237b3.mp4?t=1680275362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Charming main character!<br><br>• Simplicity!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072910/extras/0e83ae5d2a9fd7b235839d535f878117.poster.avif?t=1680275362\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072910/extras/0e83ae5d2a9fd7b235839d535f878117.webm?t=1680275362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072910/extras/0e83ae5d2a9fd7b235839d535f878117.mp4?t=1680275362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Nostalgia!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072910/extras/996ee5bc